prompt_template:
Create a {ASPECT_RATIO} raster poster in the "Scarlet Megatype Action Collage Style" visual style.

Subject: {SUBJECT}
Action: {SUBJECT_ACTION}
Prop/Product: {PRODUCT_OR_PROP}
Location: {LOCATION}
Background: {BACKGROUND_ELEMENTS}
Main text: {MAIN_TEXT}
Secondary text: {SECONDARY_TEXT}
Accent symbol: {ACCENT_SYMBOL}
Wardrobe/styling: {WARDROBE_STYLE}
Style fidelity anchors: {STYLE_FIDELITY_ANCHORS}
Source content to avoid: {SOURCE_CONTENT_TO_AVOID}

Apply these style rules:
- Composition: saturated scarlet red field, enormous cropped off-white condensed uppercase wordforms running diagonally through the frame, one heroic foreground photo-cutout subject, two or three smaller supporting cutouts, and a compact upper-corner information lockup with a simple black icon.
- Perspective: low wide-angle action perspective with aggressive foreshortening; limbs, tools, vehicles, fabric, or props can break toward the viewer; keep the subject integrated with a flat poster plane.
- Typography: blunt industrial condensed uppercase sans-serif, huge diagonal main type behind the action, tight stacked corner type, short stat-like secondary label, mostly white and black, legible and unsmeared.
- Color: scarlet red dominates, warm off-white carries the ground and mega-type, black adds icons, labels, and shadows, photographic tones are muted and pushed into a red-black campaign grade.
- Texture and lighting: matte printed poster surface, controlled paper grain, subtle halftone, hard highlights, dense shadows, crisp cutout edges, and controlled motion blur only on fast-moving props.
- Graphic elements: diagonal speed slashes, angular underlines, stark cast shadows, simple icon silhouette, and spare campaign-code details.

Avoid all source content and marks named in the source-content field. Do not use soccer, football, Canada, maple leaves, real team logos, brand marks, watermarks, QR codes, signatures, or the original phrases. Match the style fidelity anchors first, then change the subject, action, prop, scene, text, and story premise.
